dc_description_s: This data set is a point shapefile of centroids of Public Land Survey System (PLSS) units ranging from Townships to Quarter-Quarter-Sections. The data are derived from the Wisconsin DNR's 'Landnet' database, automated from 1:24,000-scale sources.In December, 2016, GIS Section staff corrected erroneous Landnet code values in points contributing to errors in landnet quarter quarter NESE3342N14W
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. for the most current data available, visit: https://data-wi-dnr.opendata.arcgis.com/ [A reference document, '24K Landnet Spatial Database Technical Documentation', 1996, Wisconsin DNR, includes details about the sources and characteristics of the 24K Landnet database:http://www.dnr.state.wi.us/maps/gis/documents/landnet_doc.pdf ]
